Name: UCSB
Description: A great University along the California Coast !

Name: Inverness House
Description: A beautiful home, built by my parents and completed around 2009. I grew up around the construction and once the house was finished lived here until I graduated highschool.

Name: Grandma and Granpa's House
Description: Built by my grandfather in the 90s, this home is where my mother's parents spent their retiremnet until their death.

Name: Dance Studio
Description: This building was first Ballet Petit, then VHC, then Inspire Dance Studio. I danced here from age 12 to age 17, and grew a lot personally, emmotionally, and artistically within the building.

Name: Memorial Park
Description: The main park in my hometown, I have many memories here throughout my childhood and adolecent life.

Name: Descanso House
Description: While I only lived here for a short while before moving out to college, my family currently lives here. It is there home and the place I stay when I go back to my hometown to visit.
